title: GRIMM.S03E01-S03E04 Eng srt -Lindoff
description:
"Grimm" -- When homicide detective Nick Burkhardt is paid a visit by his sick aunt, he gets an explanation for all of the strange things he has been seeing. She informs him that they are "Grimms," hunters charged with protecting humanity from supernatural creatures. Nick looks further into her past and discovers that he too must bear the responsibility of his ancestors and deal with the mythology of the Brothers Grimm. As Burkhardt tries to hide the dangers of his newfound calling from his fiancee and his partner, he gets more entrenched in the ancient rivalries of the Grimm world.

 Russell Hornsby.......... as Hank Griffin
